changelog: Updated to 1.18.2
Added swing speed setting to Hand View and separated hand settings
Fixed axolotls not being under water animals
.toggle all command now also toggles HUD
Renamed Vanilla Spoof to Server Spoof and added resource pack spoofing setting
Added button to import proxies from a file
Modules can now be marked as favorite
Fixed Search incorrectly rendering fluids
Fixed wireframe entity rendering with high coordinates
Added shader more to Storage ESP
Added ignore passive to Kill Aura
Added setting to display trajectories of already existing entities to Trajectories
Improved Arrow Dodge
Added Tunnel ESP
Removed mojang accounts from account manager
Fixed compatibility with Better Ping Display
Added gamemode setting to Better Tab
Added commits checker to meteor and addons, opens when clicking on the credits line in main menu
Fixed Ghost Hand
Added render original setting to Blink
Settings command (.s kill-aura) now opens the module screen
Fixed crash with Auto Smelter
A lot of other bug fixes and small tweaks
